        "TileImage": "$($repository c6b75baf-c406-468a-89d7-6137ecaef067).Image",
        "Description": "This magnificent hotel with its stunning views counts some of the scum of the earth among its guests. Corrupt politicians, businessmen, mobsters... And although these people are normally our targets, this time we&apos;re focussing on the staff. This hotel has been infiltrated by an elite team of spies named the Vultures - who gather sensitive information and sell it to the highest bidder. And no one ever takes the cleaning crew into account.",
